# 副簽
(pos:名詞)
<explanation>
yue:主要簽名旁邊嘅次要簽名（量詞：個）
eng:counter-signature
<eg>
yue:份合約要佢哋兩個一齊簽，先至有效，所以佢要簽個副簽。 (fan3 wun3 ze3 jiu6 keoi5 dei5 loeng5 go3 jat1 cai1 cin1, sin1 zi6 jau5 hou6, so2 ji5 keoi5 jiu6 cin1 go3 fu6 cin1.)
eng:This contract needs both of them to sign together to be valid, so he needs to add a counter-signature. [end of text]


